  <h1>Best Burr Coffee Grinder Under 200 (2026): 6 Top Picks</h1>
  <p class="lead">The best burr coffee grinder under 200 for most people is the Baratza Encore ESP because it balances reliable filter consistency with genuinely usable entry-espresso control. We compared six popular models by grind quality, retention/static behavior, cleanup burden, and value so you can choose once and stop replacing mediocre grinders.</p>

