      { category: 'Manual', tagline: 'Maximum grind quality per dollar', icon: 'hand', color: '#8B6F47', features: ['Steel conical burrs', 'Zero motor noise', 'Travel-ready size', 'Wide brew range'], topPick: 'KINGrinder K6', price: '$', subtitle: 'Hand-ground precision', asin: 'B09WH9JKY1' },
    ]}
    footer="coffeegearlab.com - burr grinders under $200 - 2026"
  />

  <p><strong>Quick answer:</strong> Buy Baratza Encore ESP for the best all-around value. OXO Brew Conical Burr is the best budget-first pick, Fellow Opus is the best mid-range all-rounder, and Turin SK40 is the best espresso-leaning choice before you cross the $200 line.</p>

