  <p>Where Opus shines is day-to-day livability: compact size, decent retention behavior, and an overall workflow that feels modern. It is not the easiest model to master instantly, but once you understand its adjustment pattern, it becomes a dependable all-rounder in this budget bracket.</p>
  <p><CtaButton href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BV96VPSR/ref=nosim?tag=coffee-site-20" external>Check Price on Amazon</CtaButton></p>

